# Workflow Shortcuts

- `$plan-feature` to create `PLAN.md` and `FILE_SPECS.md` before coding.
- `$build-feature` to implement the approved plan with subagents and closeout steps.
- `$verify-feature` to run verification and update `VERIFY.md`.
- `$review-feature` to run final review and update `REVIEW.md`.

